LLM_response_editer_en:
To select all text, we do not need to use the mouse operation, but can directly use keyboard shortcuts. The following operations are for selecting all text:```json
[
    {"action_type": "KeyboardAction", "keyboard_action_type": "press", "keyboard_key": "Control_L+a"}
]
```

